_sText:
I kept and added to the skeleton of my old map, dm_tunnels_v2. This map features realistic textures, added water in the small trenches, and it is a little bit darker giving it a creepy feel. Please download and try my map. Rate it and give me feedback if you can. Thank you.

New Features in V3:
- Water in trenches
- Slightly darker
- Realistic textures
- Custom made NAV file for bots
- Texture errors fixed
